pmac
----
proper MAC address generator and changer

Tomas Cech <sleep_walker@suse.cz>
2012

The main purpose of this tool is to fake your hardware address (MAC) for WiFi networks like Internet coffees, open networks and similar. It should generate random but believable addresses.

For usage check manpage.

License is GPLv2.

You can find recent version on GitHub:

https://sleep-walker@github.com/sleep-walker/pmac.git
